{"tid":2388432,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"充滿異國的氣質！韓國演藝圈混血出身的藝人們，每位都有自己獨特的魅力～","createTime":"2021-01-31T06:29:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-31T07:45:08.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f6384e381aad94624db6f6459f5b38812e50c36a","tid":2388432,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T06:29:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_c73618710be960ec46349926f9908741/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-01-28/133322-895065.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_c73618710be960ec46349926f9908741%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-01-28%2F133322-895065.jpg&h=5ce3e451&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nSEVENTEEN中Vernon的深邃大眼，真的很像年輕時候的「李奧納多」呢！<br />\n<br />\n｜康男<br />\n從在日本以搖滾團體出道，後來又到韓國擔任M.I.B主唱的康男，其實父親是日本人，而「康男」其實也是他的日文名字，發音跟韓文一樣，雖然小時候在日本長大，不過高中時曾到夏威夷留學，認識了很多韓國朋友，才學會了韓文。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_9759031d2ba5fad63ece689f08991180/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-01-28/133322-895066.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_9759031d2ba5fad63ece689f08991180%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-01-28%2F133322-895066.jpg&h=29486e03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(圖片或影片來源：IG@kangkangnam)<br />\n<br />\n｜全昭彌<br />\n由I.O.I限定組合出道，現在以個人SOLO活動的全昭彌，父親身為荷蘭裔加拿大人，所以擁有三種血統的全昭彌，從小長相就非常凸顯，也曾因為這樣而被孤立過，不過現在的高人氣，也再度證明了相信自己就是最美的！<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_f27b9342ca27d92b5482f4fbcdd10110/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-01-28/133322-895067.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_f27b9342ca27d92b5482f4fbcdd10110%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-01-28%2F133322-895067.jpg&h=755431db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(圖片或影片來源：IG@somsomi0309)<br />\n<br />\n｜MOMOLAND Nancy<br />\nMOMOLAND中的「忙內」Nancy，小時候出生於韓國，而爸爸是美國俄亥俄州人，所以2歲時搬到美國生活，後來9歲時回到韓國，小小年紀就以音樂劇而出道，後來更是成為MOMOLAND的一員。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_bd827c79097b8c8aae9acf7de966176a/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-01-28/133322-895068.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_bd827c79097b8c8aae9acf7de966176a%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-01-28%2F133322-895068.jpg&h=eee84c9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(圖片或影片來源：IG@nancyjewel_mcdonie_)<br />\n<br />\n｜SEVENTEEN Vernon<br />\n看過一眼就難忘記帥氣模樣的Vernon，母親是法裔美國人，而Vernon出眾的外貌讓他在中學時就被星探發掘，而成為練習生，更在經歷的選拔後，以男團SEVENTEEN出道，雖然比起英文韓文更擅長，不過因為母親不會說韓語，所以在家中還是會用英文溝通呢～<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_713cfba3c83b69b5ed4ab98a0677d7b2/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-01-28/133322-895069.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_713cfba3c83b69b5ed4ab98a0677d7b2%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-01-28%2F133322-895069.jpg&h=020e74c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5b6857e7e1062a31c2be680485399a1e15cd869a","tid":2388432,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T06:31:33.000Z","msg":"帥...？"},{"pid":"08931c9e2e3ffc1e5add88cb9bf5bf59dca4c1d9","tid":2388432,"uid":320204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T06:42:28.000Z","msg":"nancy屁股唔錯 又幾靚 想色<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aac336b46eed61ec6435df2b157de0ff9e5ca1f1","tid":2388432,"uid":106212,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T07:45:08.000Z","msg":"日韓混血就收皮啦<br />\n成日覺得呢啲黃種人圍內混血嘅都攞出嚟講好on9 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}